summary: Retex of the mask part with the skull from Emile\'s helmet.
descriptionHtml:
If anything goes wrong, it\'s not my fault, take no responsibility, etc.

A simple retexture of the mask part of the Nightingale armor to add the carved skull from Emile\'s helmet from Halo Reach. Male and Female.

The rest of the Nightingale armor you see is the assassins creed mod, i only replaced the cape texture for the pictures.
author: Matt Martin
